title: Average retail price for butter in Canada 2015 to 2019
summary: This grouped bar chart represents Average retail price in CAD on the Y-axis. And, its value throughout 12 Months for 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018, and 2019.
All through the Months, similar trend was observed for 2019 and 2018. In both cases, the Average retail price in CAD have increased.
In Month Jul, 2019 had the highest Average retail price in CAD 516.0 among the 5 groups and in Jul, 2015 had the lowest Average retail price in CAD 46.0.
In Month Jul, 2019 had the highest Average retail price in CAD among all 12 Months and it has the lowest Average retail price in CAD in Month Dec.
